**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.dockerignore
# .editorconfig is required inside the Docker build context: it carries the
# project-wide analyzer severity overrides (MA0048, CA1716, CA1000, …). Without
# it, `dotnet publish -c Release` re-promotes those warnings via
# TreatWarningsAsErrors=true and the image build fails (F9 k6-smoke regression).
